You, beautiful boss babe. 
You have permission to want what you want. 
All those thoughts that keep trying to convince you of anything else are lies.

Those are stories someone told you along the way.

It's ok to drop those stories now.

That's all they are. Stories. Lies.

You can change your mind right now. 
It's sexy to want want you want. 
What do you want?

Why is it important for you to want this?

What does wanting this allow you to do? Be? Become?

Where the mind goes, life follows. When we focus upon something, we align to that. Often much of what we focus on subconsciously isn't even recognized. It isn't about controlling or suppressing our behaviors. It's more about creating new ones. Deep down if you fear dying, part of you will continue to create situations to conquer it or come close to it. It's a secret wish so you can make peace with death. Our karmas impact our thinking as well. The #Buddha said action reaction. What you expect or put out, returns. Jesus taught yes this is true but in a moment of grace all is forgiven. It is not that we are given full grace for our misaligned thoughts and actions. We are given grace to use the God force to erase our debts when we have a full heart of clarity and surrender. It is when we let go of the past and understand it. When we face our fears and connect to a new path of energy. It isn't as simple to think positive. That will get you some relatively cool small things. It's about connecting your energies to grace and #compassion for yourself and others. It's an internal #permission to no longer have to suffer while releasing the feeling of being owed something better. When you #surrender higher, then you begin to assume that everything that shows up is reflecting something of value to you. Then you can decide what to do with that information. Go into the fear. Be curious like an observer and explore. It will lose hold of you when you realize death isn't possible. When you understand fear is a #secret wish, then you will give yourself that healing. #healingyourself #confrontyourdemons #spirituality #davidmamet #deepquotes

First, I asked my fellow #seeker what they envisioned for themselves on our journey together. What words, colors, and images were most #present. --
I then proceeded to guide us to a space of experiencing how the 6 month journey would unfold.
--
To decondition ones mind is to cease analyzing its original conditioning, we declared.
--
This declaration was rooted in knowledge that visions & answers to questions are of no real value. But they do serve a purpose in illuminating the #power of the mind .... and where it chooses to place #focus.
--
It's truly all about mind training, you see. The AWAKEN journey. You declare what you'll experience, and the mind has your back. It almost ..... BECOMES #ready. You grant it #permission to be effortless  @aimeeeoff
--
